  "original_title": "BRICS \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db5\u0dbd\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Chinese Foreign Minister says BRICS is effective",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese State Minister and Foreign Minister Wang Yi says the Chinese hosting year at BRICS has been fruitful so far.",
        "Wang made the remarks after concluding a series of meetings on BRICS hosted by China, which will chair the mechanism in 2022.",
        "This collection is made up of China, Russia, India, Brazil and South Africa, and is a challenging alliance for the world powers.",
        "BRICS stands for Emerging Market Group in Brazil, Russia, India, China and South Africa."
      ],
